            "title": "美股3大指數及羅素2000俱創新高　英特爾急升近23%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數，及反映細價股表現的羅素2000指數都創收市新高。美國聯儲局重啟減息，市場信心增加。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數高開38點後，升幅擴大至最多299點，最高報46317點；收報46142點，升124點，升幅0.27%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數收報6631點，升31點，升幅0.48%，曾漲0.86%，至6656點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數收報22470點，升209點，升幅0.94%，一度抽升1.26%，至22540點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羅素2000指數升2.5%，是去年11月以來首次創收市新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">個別股份方面，Nvidia宣布以50億美元入股晶片製造商英特爾，帶動英特爾股價急升22.8%收市，創1987年10月以來最大單日升幅。Nvidia升逾3% ;同業 超微半導體(AMD)股價曾跌5.8%，收市跌0.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他大型科技股走勢不一，Tesla跌逾2%，Meta靠穩，亞馬遜收市變動不大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》報道，日本銀行三井住友考慮增持投行富瑞(Jefferies)股權至約20%，富瑞股價急升5.8%。Caterpillar升3.6%，為升幅最大道指成份股；Visa回吐2.3%，為表現最差道指成份股。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15273180-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a13%e5%a4%a7%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e5%8f%8a%e7%be%85%e7%b4%a02000%e4%bf%b1%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e8%8b%b1%e7%89%b9%e7%88%be%e6%80%a5%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%9123",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-19 08:40:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "德股高收近1.4%  英國維持利率不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲3大指數上升，聯儲局重啟減息，推動大市表現，半導體相關股份表現較好。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈0.8%，報555點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報9228點，升19點，升幅0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報7854點，升67點，升幅0.87%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報23674點，升315點，升幅1.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報42307點，升0.84%或352點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報15175點，升0.32%或48點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國央行議息後公布，維持利率在4厘水平不變，符合市場預期，稱未來減息取決於通脹下降之勢是否持續，稱「循序漸進、小心謹慎」的做法仍然合適。英鎊偏軟。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15273178-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e8%bf%911-4-%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%81%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%87%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%8a",
